title: #92Noon at #KFANCombine: Cossell/Caplan/Turner/Spielman/Schrager/Musgrave
description: PA, Charch and Nordo are back at the NFL combine! NFL Films' Greg Cossell stops by, former Vikings OC Norv Turner returns to #92Noon, Vikings GM Rick Spielman talks about the Vikings QB situation, Cowboys OC Scott Linehan joins the show, NFL Networks Peter Schrager talks with PA and Charch, and Broncos OC Bill Musgrave swings by to talk football!
